description:
Danny welcomes the brilliant Ronnie Karam (from the Watch What Crappens & Rose Pricks podcast) to recap episode 4 of MTV's Lohan Beach Club. They discuss Jonitta and Gabi's explosive fight, Lindsay comparing herself to Tomb Raider, and more. Danny also recaps this week's amazing #RHONJ, where a fight breaks out between Marge & Danielle at dinner.


Ronnie Karam: 1:48ish

#RHONJ: 46:49ish
